Package: ev3dev-tools
Architecture: all
Depends: flash-kernel, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Miscellaneous tools for ev3dev
 * ev3dev-config:    A graphical command line utility to help with basic system administration.
 * ev3dev-sysinfo:   Command line utility to display system information.
 * ev3dev-powerinfo: Prints power supply information
